%% 3.2.2 Delete Student — sequence (layered)

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Actor as Admin
    participant UI as UI (Student Detail)
    participant SC as Controller (StudentController)
    participant SS as Service (StudentService)
    participant Repo as Repository (IRepository Student)
    participant DB as Database (SQL Server)

    Actor->>UI: Confirm Delete
    UI->>SC: DELETE /api/Student/Delete/{id}
    SC->>SS: DeleteStudentAsync(id)

    alt Has active orders or trips (spec — implement guard)
        SS->>Repo: Check related Order StudentBusAssignment ...
        Repo->>DB: SELECT
        SS-->>SC: throw conflict
        SC-->>UI: 400
        UI-->>Actor: Cannot delete — active subscriptions
    else Allowed
        SS->>Repo: Delete(student)
        Repo->>DB: DELETE
        SS-->>SC: OK
        SC-->>UI: 200
        UI->>UI: Router → Student Roster
    end
